title: Nike Original Run- The Hives- Black, White, and Run (320kbps)
description:
The Hives- Black, White and Run (Nike Original Run)

Continuous Mix

Wall of guitars? Check. Propulsive percussion? Absolutely. Rally-cry lyrics? Of course. The Hives' signature sound comes to bear in this inspired Nike+ Original Remix.  Pulling elements from The Hives' smash hit The Black and White Album, the production duo, Expensive People, craft a completely new running adventure.  This 45-minute journey begins with a steady warm-up and then allows the runner to find his/her stride before culminating in a fast-paced, high-energy explosion.   The run closes with a restorative cool-down and leaves fans with a newfound appreciation for this iconic Swedish rock band.

Runners take their cues from the changes in tempo, instinctively picking up the pace when the music intensifies, catching a breather as the beats slow down.  You can use Black, White and Run for tempo runs or simply as motivation to add a few bursts of speed to your regular runs.  Elements from "Tick Tick Boom", "Try It Again", "Won't Be Long' and others show up in this audio odyssey, delivering the vocals you love remixed to create the ultimate runner's companion.
